## ðŸ§  System Overview

| Layer | Purpose |
|-----|--------|
| **StacksWorth Hub (`stx-hub`)** | Local Python FastAPI service exposing unified JSON endpoints for Bitcoin, BitAxe, and system metrics |
| **StacksWorth UI** | Fullscreen HTML / CSS / JS dashboard rendered in Chromium kiosk mode |
| **Bitcoin Node** | Native `bitcoind` running on SSD; primary blockchain and mempool source |
| **BitAxe Integration** | Local polling of BitAxe devices for hashrate, temperature, shares, and status |
| **Host System** | Raspberry Pi OS Lite (64-bit) optimized for kiosk and node workloads |

